---
---
<!-- Section 4 — Comment ça marche (fond clair) -->
<section class="section-light section-pad">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <div class="label-caps gs-hidden" data-gs="s4" data-gs-delay="0" style="color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:20px;text-align:center;">Comment &ccedil;a fonctionne</div>
    <h2 class="h1 gs-hidden" data-gs="s4" data-gs-delay="0.1" style="color:var(--text-light-primary);max-width:700px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;">Un syst&egrave;me de relance autonome</h2>
    <p class="lead gs-hidden" data-gs="s4" data-gs-delay="0.15" style="color:var(--text-light-primary);max-width:520px;margin-top:16px;font-weight:400;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;">Vous gardez votre logiciel et votre fa&ccedil;on d'envoyer vos devis.</p>

    <!-- Pipeline flow -->
    <div class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s4" data-gs-delay="0.2" style="margin-top:72px;max-width:960px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
      <div class="flow-pipeline">
        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="flow-card">
            <div class="flow-badge">01</div>
            <div class="flow-desc">Vous continuez &agrave; envoyer vos devis normalement.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-connector"><div class="flow-connector-line"></div><div class="flow-connector-arrow"></div></div>
        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="flow-card flow-card-highlight">
            <div class="flow-badge flow-badge-highlight">02</div>
            <div class="flow-desc">Notre syst&egrave;me d&eacute;tecte l'envoi du devis et d&eacute;clenche les relances.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-connector"><div class="flow-connector-line"></div><div class="flow-connector-arrow"></div></div>
        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="flow-card">
            <div class="flow-badge">03</div>
            <div class="flow-desc">D&egrave;s qu'un prospect r&eacute;pond ou signe, le suivi s'arr&ecirc;te.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:64px;">
        <span style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text-light-primary);font-weight:500;">Vous ne modifiez pas vos habitudes. Le syst&egrave;me s'adapte &agrave; vos outils.</span>
        <div style="margin-top:32px;">
          <button style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:14px 26px;border-radius:11px;font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:#1D5FBF;color:#FFFFFF;transition:background 0.2s ease,transform 0.2s ease,box-shadow 0.2s ease;box-shadow:0px 10px 25px rgba(29,95,191,0.35);" onclick="document.getElementById('section-callback').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})" onmouseover="this.style.background='#174EA6';this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)';this.style.boxShadow='0px 14px 32px rgba(29,95,191,0.45)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#1D5FBF';this.style.transform='translateY(0)';this.style.boxShadow='0px 10px 25px rgba(29,95,191,0.35)'">
            Demander sa place &rarr;
          </button>
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-light-secondary);margin-top:10px;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Phase limit&eacute;e &agrave; 100 entreprises</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 5 — Notre Différence (fond clair) -->
<section class="section-light section-pad" style="background:var(--bg-light-alt);border-top:1px solid var(--border-light);">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <div class="label-caps gs-hidden" data-gs="s5" data-gs-delay="0" style="color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:20px;text-align:center;">Notre diff&eacute;rence</div>
    <h2 class="h1 gs-hidden" data-gs="s5" data-gs-delay="0.1" style="color:var(--text-light-primary);max-width:700px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;">Des relances adapt&eacute;es au comportement du prospect</h2>
    <p class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s5" data-gs-delay="0.15" style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:17px;color:var(--text-light-secondary);max-width:560px;margin:20px auto 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.65;">Il ne s'agit pas d'envoyer plus de relances.<br>Il s'agit d'envoyer la bonne relance, au bon moment.</p>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:56px;">
      <div class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s5" data-gs-delay="0.2" style="background:var(--bg-light-card);border:1px solid var(--border-light);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 22px;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 20V10"/><path d="M18 20V4"/><path d="M6 20v-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:var(--text-light-primary);letter-spacing:-0.01em;">Des relances qui &eacute;voluent</h3>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--text-light-secondary);margin-top:14px;line-height:1.65;">Ouverture, clic, r&eacute;ponse ou absence d'activit&eacute; : la relance suivante s'ajuste automatiquement en fonction des donn&eacute;es.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s5" data-gs-delay="0.3" style="background:var(--bg-light-card);border:1px solid var(--border-light);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 22px;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3"/><path d="M16 8V2h6"/><path d="M22 2L12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:var(--text-light-primary);letter-spacing:-0.01em;">Le bon canal selon le contexte</h3>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--text-light-secondary);margin-top:14px;line-height:1.65;">Email, SMS ou WhatsApp : le canal utilis&eacute; d&eacute;pend du moment et de l'engagement du prospect.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s5" data-gs-delay="0.4" style="background:var(--bg-light-card);border:1px solid var(--border-light);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 22px;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--accent-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:var(--text-light-primary);letter-spacing:-0.01em;">L'exp&eacute;rience de la relance</h3>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:15px;color:var(--text-light-secondary);margin-top:14px;line-height:1.65;">Nous faisons &eacute;voluer nos s&eacute;quences de relances en analysant chaque client, pour obtenir le meilleur r&eacute;sultat.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s5" data-gs-delay="0.5" style="margin-top:56px;padding-top:48px;border-top:1px solid var(--border-light);max-width:720px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(20px,2.2vw,26px);letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text-light-primary);line-height:1.4;">Le suivi s'adapte au prospect jusqu'&agrave; sa d&eacute;cision.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
